722212f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 47th Street
722212f-a.text:
Park Avenue, north from 47th Street, showing east side.
On the east side, going north is shown the Park Lane (1924). The
Railroad Y.M.C.A. (1913-1929) hides St. Bartholomew's Church
(1919). The Ambassador Hotel (1920) follows, between 5lst and
52nd Streets.
